    "Regulation, banning, and close supervision have also been recommended as strategies to mitigate the threats of Chat-GPT in previous studies (see Rahman & Watanobe 2023 and Kalhan 2023).",
    "Overall, these rich empirical findings can be a valuable source of information for schools and universities trying to formulate institutional guidelines for integrating and regulating AI writing tools in education.",
    "These findings will also be our basis for creating a set of recommendations to safeguard established standards in teaching and research.",
    "By and large, the identified educators' concerns may offer an explanation for why they have ambivalent reactions to these emerging technologies that revolutionize education.",
    "In addition to lack of training, support, and access to the efficient and ethical use of tools, these concerns prevent them from maximizing the tools."
